title: this app needs to get their stuff together
review: lovely app for the most part but they love to ban accounts, and they will do so without telling you why. just because people with lots of viewers get reported because their little fans get mad and snapchat doesnt even look into it. not to mention they refuse to give you an actual way to contact them other than through the support link on their website which is a bit absurd. i have problems id like to address and they dont even wanna hear about it.

title: Snapchat
review: Snapchat is just overall amazing. It’s the best app I’ve ever used. I love it! Keep up the good work..

title: Mass Delete friends
review: I love the app but I would suggest snap to add a mass delete friends option because I have way too many people that I don’t talk to and some are just bots, I would suggest Snapchat to do something like that

title: sending snaps!
review: I use Snapchat all the time it’s probably the app I use most on my phone and overall it’s a great app!! And if you have Snapchat you probably know what streaks are (sending a snap to keep a snap streak going with friends). But it would really help if you could click more friends at once like maybe if there was a “select all” button I’m not sure but it would really help!!
